  {
    name: "Ken Bulmahn",
    quote: "I drove over 4 hours to do business with him and he is the only person that I will do coin business with in the future.",
    rating: 5
  },
  {
    name: "Matthew Almanza",
    quote: "David's prices are the best in the treasure valley bar none... Don't waste your time anywhere else, seriously.",
    rating: 5
  },
  {
    name: "Shea",
    quote: "Honestly, the best coin and bullion shop I've ever been to... David is top notch and runs his business on integrity.",
    rating: 5
  },
  {
    name: "Sam Farnum",
    quote: "When a man is passionate about what he does... it's almost impossible not to have a great experience.",
    rating: 5
  },
  {
    name: "Robert Sharpe",
    quote: "David is above ALL of them in his dealings when it comes to buying from me.",
    rating: 5
  },
  {
    name: "Judy Rust",
    quote: "Best shop I have been in since I've lived in Idaho. I will definitely be a regular customer.",
    rating: 5
